{"tid":1040779,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"涉盜富士精工商業機密　中國男子在日本被捕","createTime":"2019-02-28T10:34:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-28T11:11:42.000Z","uid":75969,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"5d72de4d800a7df7036631e58f71d79774534812","tid":1040779,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T10:34:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190228/s00004/022ad4f3f8bf45e2b9895fa75a6639b9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190228%2Fs00004%2F022ad4f3f8bf45e2b9895fa75a6639b9.jpg&h=9f607e8e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n31歲中國籍男子申永輝涉嫌今年1月在日本盜取商業機密，周三（27日）被愛知縣警方以違反《反不正當競爭法》罪名拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n申永輝2014年4月起，於愛知縣豐田市一家專門生產切割工具的廠商「富士精工」工作。警方指，申永輝涉嫌今年1月29日進入公司伺服器電腦，並以USB隨身碟，複製用以生產汽車零件的鑽孔機設計圖和說明書等。<br />\n<br />\n富士精工在1月30日發現複製記錄，並在本月15日報警，稱「中國籍員工似乎複製了機密信息」，最後警方於周三拘捕申永輝。警方稱，申永輝已承認曾複製有關文件，但他強調目的在於學習，並非圖利。警方又認為，有關商業機密可能已流向國外，當局將展開調查。<br />\n<br />\n富士精工於1958年成立。主要生產製造汽車零件的機牀工具，日本汽車龍頭豐田是其主要客戶之一。<br />\n<br />\n（共同社）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/兩岸/article/20190228/s00004/1551345884771/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E5%85%A9%E5%B2%B8%2Farticle%2F20190228%2Fs00004%2F1551345884771%2F&d=HVFDXqn9keSrFxh6Mt7Td9T2hWdA4JmoO%2FtHFZtOkv0%3D&h=87bb930b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E5%85%A9%E5%B2%B8%2Farticle%2F20190228%2Fs00004%2F1551345884771%2F&h=1535e2e6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/兩岸/article/20190228/s00004/1551345884771/</a>"},{"pid":"7634edcdec4189a50e472a0a8db26d5f31a27ddb","tid":1040779,"uid":4178,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T10:39:30.000Z","msg":"下年強國原創汽車更上一層樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49f58961dd7ac5f6aa3e471edbe91110ae69c103","tid":1040779,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019